TemperatureAdjuster - Interface in aquarium.hw
The TemperatureAdjuster is an interface to a device that can either raise or lower the temperature of the water in the aquarium.
TemperatureAdjuster.AdjusterState - Enum in aquarium.hw
This enumeration is a simple set of values that indicate the possible states of a TemperatureAdjuster.
TemperatureSensor - Interface in aquarium.hw
The TemperatureSensor is a sensor that tests water temperature.
